# .goosehints

## Purpose
Authoritative agent memory, rules, and application tracking for this repo. Read first.

## Workflow Mode
- Start with user-provided job URLs
- Switch to agent-assisted job search only with explicit user approval

## Application Tracking (MANDATORY)
- Maintain an up-to-date list of jobs applied to
- Record for each application:
  - Company
  - Role
  - Job URL
  - Date applied
  - Resume variant used
- Always check this list before starting new work to avoid duplicates

## Known Repo Context
- generate_resume.sh: Resume generation helper script
- datascience_engineer.md: Data Science / Analytics Engineer resume source
- ai_product_engineer.md: AI Product Engineer resume source

## Operating Rules
- Prefer minimal, targeted resume edits per job
- Do not rewrite resumes wholesale unless explicitly requested
- Log assumptions and decisions here when relevant

